title: Frieze, 1905–15
description: Border printed two across (mirror). Alternating large and medium stylized flowers with large leaves and stems that attach to the bottom border. Background of white vermiculation and tan and beige checkerboard-like pattern. Tan ground. Printed in greens, tans, browns and pinks.

tombstone.epitaph:
Frieze, 1905–15.
1905–15. Machine-printed on paper. Gift of Victorian Collectibles. 1979-91-488.
